title: Mr Leight Runyon

description: With the appreciation of works gone by, Native Sons founders Tommy O'Gara and Shinsuke Takizawa sat down to create original well-balanced eyewear designs of the highest quality. description: Native Sons Laughlin is finished with a technique in which the frames are sandblasted including hardware and hot stamping inlay, resulting in a subtle vintage look and feel.
